Rating: 3
This was a wonderful surprise and a great way to use up leftover ham. I added a bit more ham and cheese than the recipe called for. When it came out of the oven it was golden, creamy, and not at all rubbery, a problem I have sometimes had with polenta in the past. We had it for dinner, but it would also make a terrific brunch dish.

